INSERT IGNORE INTO Episode VALUES ('Esref Ruya', 1, 3, 'Episode 3', 'After İzzet’s death, Eşref now faces an even greater enemy. Horrified by everything that’s happened, Nisan prepares to make bold moves beyond her limits in order to finally end the game. Meanwhile, with his plans progressing as intended, Kadir is willing to betray the Yetimler to eliminate Eşref from the picture. On the law enforcement side, Serdar investigates the murder at the hotel and comes face to face with Eşref and the tribe. This tense confrontation—where everything could fall apart at any moment—sets the stage for an impending major conflict. Though Nisan plans to throw Eşref into the fire to save herself, seeing a different side of him pushes her into an unexpected dilemma. Her growing closeness with Eşref is about to land her in serious trouble.', 137);
